q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (Operational definitions must be OBSERVABLE and MEASURABLE.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 701 Td (Define behaviors so ANY observer would record them the same way.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 681 Td (1. Off-Task Behavior) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 667 Td (Eyes not directed at instructional materials, teacher, or relevant task for 3+) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 655 Td (consecutive seconds.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 637 Td (2. Verbal Disruption) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 623 Td (Any vocalization \(talking, humming, calling out\) without teacher permission) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 611 Td (that interrupts instruction.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 593 Td (3. Physical Aggression) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 579 Td (Any instance of hitting, kicking, pushing, biting, or throwing objects at) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 567 Td (another person.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 549 Td (4. Non-Compliance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 535 Td (Failure to initiate a teacher-directed task within 10 seconds of the) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 523 Td (instruction being given.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 505 Td (5. Elopement) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 491 Td (Leaving designated area \(seat, classroom, or assigned space\) without permission.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 473 Td (6. Property Destruction) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 459 Td (Any action that damages or attempts to damage materials, furniture, or others') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 447 Td (belongings.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 429 Td (7. Self-Stimulatory Behavior) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 415 Td (Repetitive motor movements \(hand flapping, rocking, spinning\) lasting 5+) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 403 Td (seconds.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 385 Td (8. Verbal Aggression) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 371 Td (Threats, insults, profanity, or intimidating statements directed at peers or) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 359 Td (adults.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 341 Td (9. Task Refusal) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 60 327 Td (Verbally stating 'no' or putting head down when presented with academic work.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 309 Td (10. Positive Peer Interaction) Tj ET
